query:
INSERT INTO polling_stations (
              election_id,
              name,
              number,
              number_of_voters,
              polling_station_type,
              address,
              postal_code,
              locality
            ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
            RETURNING
              id AS "id: u32",
              election_id AS "election_id: u32",
              name,
              number,
              number_of_voters,
              polling_station_type AS "polling_station_type: _",
              address,
              postal_code,
              locality
